### Get all work orders (should be empty)
GET http://localhost:5141/work-orders

### Get all equipment (should have your existing data)
GET http://localhost:5141/equipment

### Create Work Order for Equipment ID 1
POST http://localhost:5141/work-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "equipmentId": 1,
  "title": "Belt slipping under load",
  "description": "Needs tension adjustment",
  "assignedTo": "John Smith"
}

### Create Work Order for Equipment ID 2
POST http://localhost:5141/work-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "equipmentId": 2,
  "title": "Hydraulic fluid leak",
  "description": "Small leak detected near seal",
  "assignedTo": "Mike Chen"
