### Create Work Order for Equipment ID 3
POST http://localhost:5141/work-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "equipmentId": 3,
  "title": "Calibration check needed",
  "description": "Annual precision calibration",
  "assignedTo": "Sarah Lee"
